			<h4><a id="comment_link_64447164" name="comment_link_64447164" href="//hardware.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23311752&amp;cid=64447164" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64447164)" >Re:That's Nifty, but consumer?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64447164" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64447164); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
